<template><div><h1 id="object-pick" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#object-pick" aria-hidden="true">#</a> object.pick <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/object.pick" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/v/object.pick.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM version"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://npmjs.org/package/object.pick" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/dm/object.pick.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM monthly downloads"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a>  <a href="https://npmjs.org/package/object.pick" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/dt/object.pick.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM total downloads"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://travis-ci.org/jonschlinkert/object.pick" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/travis/jonschlinkert/object.pick.svg?style=flat&amp;label=Travis" alt="Linux Build Status"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h1>
<blockquote>
<p>Returns a filtered copy of an object with only the specified keys, similar to <code v-pre>_.pick</code> from lodash / underscore.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>You might also be interested in <a href="https://github.com/jonschlinkert/object.omit" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">object.omit<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>.</p>
<h2 id="install" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#install" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Install</h2>
<p>Install with <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">npm<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>:</p>
<div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> --save object.pick
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="benchmarks" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#benchmarks" aria-hidden="true">#</a> benchmarks</h2>
<p>This is the <a href="http://jsperf.com/pick-props" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">fastest implementation<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> I tested. Pull requests welcome!</p>
<h2 id="usage" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#usage" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Usage</h2>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">var</span> pick <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">require</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'object.pick'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>

<span class="token function">pick</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token literal-property property">a</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">'a'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token literal-property property">b</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">'b'</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">'a'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">//=> {a: 'a'}</span>

<span class="token function">pick</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token literal-property property">a</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">'a'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token literal-property property">b</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">'b'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token literal-property property">c</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">'c'</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token string">'a'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">'b'</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">//=> {a: 'a', b: 'b'}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="about" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#about" aria-hidden="true">#</a> About</h2>
